o wow...summer has been such a blast so far!!
first my chica karissa picked me up on friday and we drove to san diego. we got there at like 4 or 5 and checked into the PARADISE HOTEL fun fun. and so from there we went to the pool and sat out and soaked up some cancerous UV rays...more fun. and after that we went downtown to the gaslamp part of san diego. it is sooo groovy down there!! there are like 50 streets packed w/ people and nifty little restaurants, underground clubs, and dirty lingerie stores...still more fun. and so we ate dinner at this classy little restaurant called BELLA LUNA (which in italian means beautiful moon, hah figured that one out on my own thankyou very much). and then we got back to the hotel at around 10 or 11 and i was dead tired so we hit the sack. sooo in the morning we got up early and went to SEA WORLD omg!! sooo much fun. my favorite part were the bat rays and otters. so karissa convinced me to go on atlantis and roaring rapids...these 2 awsome water ride, and we got SOAKED i mean SOAKED it looked like we had both just dove into a pool...but it was FUN!! anywho, we get back to the hotel at around 7 and decide to go to the pool and we got some junk food at the little cafe thing majiggy. and we sat in the pool and jacuzzi until like 11 and then went back to the room and watched ELLA ENCHANTED...needless to say i was wiped out the next day. so we started our long journey home and we went to this spiffy little candy store and got some yummy crap there. and then off again... the drive was sooo long and we FINALLY got home (plus my butt fell asleep a few times during the drive home).  anywho monday was my BIRTHDAY!!! yea!!! and so i went out w/ my muchachos to six flags baby!! it was sooo fun. then as the day wound down we had a "waving and saying hi" contest...and we met stalker boy and KYLE whos the coolest kid ever!!(and danielle's SUPER-MOM!!!) so then big mama pucci took us all home to bb's house and we watched gothika...fucking scary and then road trip...fucking funny.  so ya we all went to bed at like 2 in the morning...phewy im tired man. and then in the morning we had pancakes and powdered donuts for breakfast and then my momma took me and karissa home and then i came home and watched tv for a few hours and then took a nap cuz im hella tired. holy crap this is like the LONGEST post ive ever done...and ever will do, unless another weekend like this comes up. ok im outie. 
ce la vie

-me
